m said that the volunteers would visit the coronavirus infected places to for awareness raising events.\n\nSimilarly, the Ministry of Finance has released budget for 60 ICU beds. Dr Gautam stated that those ICU beds would be readied at Tribhuvan University Teaching Hospital (TUTH) and Dhulikhel Hospital.","title":"Bir Hospital is now designated for Covid-19 treatment","url":"http://english.ratopati.com/story/15131","video":[]}
